channel.title: PhyscoDev Server
channel.description:
Seeing as how my old one.. well.. broke (not world, IP), due to IP troubles. I decided to post here for anything who used to play it and for new people who wish to play it.
The IP is here, as it's dynamic and I can't afford to make it static I set up a website which will say the IP whenever it changes, along with videos of the server.
http://physcodev.webs.com/
Have fun!!
